WORK / life balance
MIND / body balance

We are a culture of imbalance
  - mind is body
  - body is mind

Feedback loops
  - tension and pain
  - anxiety and restlessness
  - fatigue and sickness
  - depression and recurring injuries
  - STOP AND LISTEN TO OUR BODIES

What Practical Things Can We Do?
  - pomodoros
    - 25 mins focused work - 5 mins break
    - stand up, move around, no screens
    - real programmers take breaks
  - longer breaks
  - exercise
  - meditation
  - food
